    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《油滑深渊》</strong> 是一款短篇恐怖游戏，故事发生在海洋深处的潜艇上。你必须确定石油的方位，前往现场开采，否则下达命令的神秘声音就会切断你的氧气供给。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>一款设计为在一小时内完成的恐怖体验</strong></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >驾驶潜艇</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你在潜艇的视野有限，充分留意各种仪表、表盘和显示器。在海底谨慎航行，寻找采油目标位点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113030/extras/31e765dda7f2b01918cb0f5ed041b157.poster.avif?t=1770899136\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113030/extras/31e765dda7f2b01918cb0f5ed041b157.webm?t=1770899136\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113030/extras/31e765dda7f2b01918cb0f5ed041b157.mp4?t=1770899136\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >操作危险的钻机</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >操作拉杆、工具，设置夹臂，等等等等。你要熟练运用所有设备，熟到闭着眼睛都能操作……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113030/extras/c70c01818ea10433bf18d3a589cce93d.poster.avif?t=1770899136\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113030/extras/c70c01818ea10433bf18d3a589cce93d.webm?t=1770899136\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113030/extras/c70c01818ea10433bf18d3a589cce93d.mp4?t=1770899136\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >务必避免溺亡、火灾或葬身鱼腹……</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这份工作需要一颗大心脏……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113030/extras/be1491cab885ca73abfd0fe8cbb912a6.poster.avif?t=1770899136\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113030/extras/be1491cab885ca73abfd0fe8cbb912a6.webm?t=1770899136\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113030/extras/be1491cab885ca73abfd0fe8cbb912a6.mp4?t=1770899136\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
